WATER BALLOONS 🎈
•
Hello guys! This must be my favourite activity at home thus far! I can touch and squish these balloons for hours on end 🤣Mummy simply filled up coloured balloons with a bit of water 💦 and taped them down on the peripheries of my cot (or more aptly, my playpen 😇)
•
It was a new experience trying to walk around the cot (with support of the rails, of course) and ‘capturing’ each balloon. Mummy asked me to gently touch and feel the balloons each time I reached one, but I much preferred to yank them out and throw them away. Maybe next time I should do javelin or short put HAHA 🤗
•
Btw I kept putting the balloons into my mouth and they tasted ewww, but it was a good chance for me to learn about a new texture AND more importantly, what not to put into my mouth! 😮
•
